{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"8d0744a3-5fae-429d-b012-5340d5e58662","content":"There's no workflow file in the current directory, so here's general guidance on switching to NuGet trusted publishing (OIDC):\n\n### 1. Configure NuGet.org\n\nOn [nuget.org](https://www.nuget.org), go to your package → **Manage** → **Publishing policies** → **Trusted Publishers**. Add a GitHub Actions publisher specifying your **repository owner**, **repository name**, **workflow filename**, and optionally an **environment**.\n\n### 2. Update your GitHub Actions workflow\n\n**Add permissions** (required for OIDC token):\n```yaml\npermissions:\n  id-token: write   # needed to request the OIDC JWT\n  contents: read\n```\n\n**Add an environment** (recommended, must match NuGet config):\n```yaml\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    environment: nuget        # must match what you registered on NuGet.org\n```\n\n**Replace** the `dotnet nuget push` step:\n```yaml\n# BEFORE (secret-based)\n- run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }} --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n\n# AFTER (trusted publishing / OIDC)\n- run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\nNo `--api-key` is needed — the NuGet CLI automatically exchanges the OIDC token when pushing to a trusted source.\n\n### 3. Remove the secret\n\nOnce verified, delete `NUGET_API_KEY` from your repo's **Settings → Secrets**.\n\n### Key benefits\n- No long-lived secrets to rotate\n- Scoped to specific workflows/environments\n- Auditable via OIDC claims\n\nWould you like me to modify a specific workflow file?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"00bb332a-0acd-457e-9f52-555d25002b65","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"There's no workflow file in the current directory. The user is asking a general question about switching from NuGet API key to trusted publishing (OIDC). Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":502,"requestId":"1006:25127A:172248A:1A4E1BF:69E81ABF"},"id":"8649c58d-c877-4ec3-80b2-1eb9ced21164","timestamp":"2026-04-22T00:48:14.402Z","parentId":"b53f0bce-90a6-4920-b03d-43bfc758564c"}
